<h4 id=3D"Program-7.3.2ProgramListingPage">7.3.2 Program Listing Page</h4>
<p><strong>User Story:</strong><br>
AS AN Admin, Master Role, or Root Admin<br>
I NEED to view a list of all programs in the system<br>
SO THAT I can manage, search, and filter programs efficiently</p>
<p><strong>Acceptance Criteria:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p><strong>Page Header:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Page Title: "Program Management"</p></li>
<li>
<p>[+ Add New Program] button (top-right)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Search bar with filter options</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Filter &amp; Search Options:</strong></p></li>
</ol>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"3f=
281a4a-a314-4359-a5cf-eaedd8093c91" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Filter/Search</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Type</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Options/Behavior</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Search</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Text Input</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Search by: Name, Description, Subject</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Type</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
