=E2=94=98
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<ol start=3D"3">
<li>
<p><strong>Clone Process:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Step 1: User clicks [Clone] button</p></li>
<li>
<p>Step 2: Modal appears with default name: "[Original Name] - Copy"</p></l=
i>
<li>
<p>Step 3: User can modify name and select clone options</p></li>
<li>
<p>Step 4: System validates unique name</p></li>
<li>
<p>Step 5: System creates new program with copied data</p></li>
<li>
<p>Step 6: User redirected to cloned Program Details Page</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Cloned Data:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>=E2=9C=85 All general information fields (except ID, Created By/Date)</p=
></li>
<li>
<p>=E2=9C=85 All stages and product associations</p></li>
<li>
<p>=E2=9C=85 Attached files (optional, checkbox selection)</p></li>
<li>
<p>=E2=9C=85 Tags (optional, checkbox selection)</p></li>
<li>
<p>=E2=9D=8C History/audit trail (new program starts fresh)</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Default Values in Cloned Program:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Name: "[Original Name] - Copy" (editable)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Status: ACTIVE (or INACTIVE if checkbox selected)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Created By: Current user</p></li>
<li>
<p>Created Date: Current timestamp</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
<h4 id=3D"Program-7.3.7ProgramDeleteFunctionality">7.3.7 Program Delete Fun=
ctionality</h4>
<p><strong>User Story:</strong><br>
AS AN Admin, Master Role, or Root Admin<br>
I NEED to delete programs that are no longer needed<br>
SO THAT the program list remains clean and relevant</p>
<p><strong>Acceptance Criteria:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p><strong>Delete Button:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Location: Program Details Page header, Program Listing Page action colum=
n</p></li>
<li>
<p>Icon: Trash icon</p></li>
<li>
<p>Label: "Delete"</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Delete Confirmation Modal:</strong></p></li>
</ol>
