<p><strong>Authorization Notes:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Trainers, Lead Region, Head Channel: Read-only access for program select=
ion during course creation</p></li>
<li>
<p>Master Role, Admin, Root Admin: Full CRUD access to programs</p></li>
<li>
<p>DMS_ADMIN: No program management access (export-only role)</p></li>
</ul>
<h4 id=3D"Program-7.3.10ProgramValidationRules">7.3.10 Program Validation R=
ules</h4>
<p><strong>Field-Level Validation:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"44=
4076a5-06b8-41cd-ad84-6ca26f9f0e44" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Field</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Validation Rule</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Error Message</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
