</div>
<p><strong>Business Logic Validation:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p><strong>Unique Name Validation:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>System checks if program name already exists</p></li>
<li>
<p>Case-insensitive comparison</p></li>
<li>
<p>Applies to both create and edit operations</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Type Consistency Validation:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Course Type must match Program Type</p></li>
<li>
<p>Example: SHINE program =E2=86=92 SHINE course type</p></li>
<li>
<p>Prevents mismatched configurations</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Stage Validation:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Minimum 1 stage required</p></li>
<li>
<p>Each stage must have unique name within program</p></li>
<li>
<p>Each stage must have at least 1 product</p></li>
<li>
<p>Products must match program type</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Status Validation:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Only ACTIVE programs available for course creation</p></li>
<li>
<p>INACTIVE programs can still be viewed and edited</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Delete Validation:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Hard delete only allowed if no associated courses</p></li>
<li>
<p>Soft delete allowed anytime</p></li>
<li>
<p>Confirmation required for all deletions</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
